	<text_base_description>Bonita Villas is a well maintained, secure building located in the heart of Spaulding Square, West Hollywood. This unit with original fixtures and trim is ideal for the buyer who is looking to design and finish their own space. The split-level open concept condo unit features a full length spacious and private balcony, recessed lighting, large walk in closet, gas fireplace, and wet bar. The bedroom and living room are separated by plantation shutters and can be left open for a large open feeling space, or closed to create separate, distinct rooms. The Bonita Villas Building HOA features a heated saltwater rooftop pool and hot tub with unreal 360 degree panoramic city and mountain views. Other attractive Building features include low HOA dues, underground parking, on-site laundry, renovated fitness center, and lobby with secure controlled entry. Bonita Villas is centrally located minutes from Hiking at Runyon Canyon, and shopping at Target, Trader Joe's. Also minutes away are the Melrose  &amp;  Fairfax shopping and dining areas, Hollywood Blvd, as well as bars, clubs and other attractions at the World Famous Sunset Strip. Do not miss out on this incredible value.  </text_base_description>
